installationInstructions.author: Jordan from SPRINGFIELD, MO
installationInstructions.title: The bin was broken
installationInstructions.content: Lifted old bin up and pulled away from door. Took new bin, placed in door and set down in place. Replaced old broken bin with new bin. Added additional bin for more storage.
